{"tid":1887574,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"今次有救了～蝗蟲主治肺結核！","createTime":"2020-02-19T15:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T19:32:26.000Z","uid":183058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18d0eb97275d2bd498be23a879c6ba56fc9107f5","tid":1887574,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地表兩大吃貨對決！蝗蟲「主治肺結核」　陸網樂翻：新冠肺炎有救了？</span><br />\n<br />\n2020年02月17日 12:27<br />\n<br />\n實習記者陳妙津／綜合報導<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n剛在年初重創東非國家的蝗災越過阿拉伯海，正肆虐與中國接壤的印度和巴基斯坦，由於蝗蟲啃所過之處幾乎寸草不生，一天足以吃掉3.5萬人份糧食，讓正飽受新冠肺炎的中國大陸對此如臨大敵。不過有不少大陸網友發現，蝗蟲雖是害蟲，卻也是中藥材中主治肺結核的良藥、美食聖品，也有人回憶起2017年山東局部蝗災時，民眾瘋搶一時，蝗災瞬間被消滅，直呼「天上飛的根本不是蝗蟲，是人民幣！」<br />\n<br />\n有大陸網友發現，《全國中草藥匯編》中明確記載，蝗蟲性味鹹、平，主治肺結核，能使人補養強壯，若作為藥材通常以全蟲入藥，也讓不少網友腦洞大開，認為或許蝗蟲也能治療新冠肺炎，並紛紛留言表示，「依據老祖宗五行相剋原則，說不定能治肺炎」、「如果能治新型肺炎的話，可以支援一下巴基斯坦，抓幾千隻回來油炸，又消滅蝗災，一舉兩得」、「中藥醫理上治肺結核，希望對新型肺炎也有效」、「根本是給新冠肺炎病人送補品」。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVPQQzB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVPQQzB.png&h=3228b007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egNfheG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FegNfheG.png&h=c572f28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158fd155c2befd77e5b8ccf0edb7e9eb9558df21","tid":1887574,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re82MO9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre82MO9.gif&h=b67f9182&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf3a91e096d4966610f12213d3d87685d4b3e6cd","tid":1887574,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"人死了，肺結核便痊癒了"},{"pid":"b781ed8ea65d47bdff94fd497dc247f07c17f69e","tid":1887574,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:28:56.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲飛入祖國就係注定用黎救國醫新冠病毒"},{"pid":"d08c271445663e6b045c285301d95b02576e2ab2","tid":1887574,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:32:26.000Z","msg":"延續我登輝煌事蹟<br />\n借位幫推<br />\n［告急］名校secret戰線要人啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887715\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887715</a>"}]}